    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-09-07T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-09-07T00:00:00-05:00" n="387" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d387">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Armstrong</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-09-07">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 7,
                                    1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have delayed answering note of minister for foreign affairs awaiting
                            any comments from you on telegram giving contents of said note. In your
                            telegram of 24th ultimo you use expression, “$1,500,000 in Spanish gold
                            pesos.” Spanish minister expresses it as “1,500,000 Spanish gold pesos.”
                            I await your comments upon this difference of words. Otherwise, entire
                            agreement between your telegram and note of minister for foreign
                            affairs.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Armstrong</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
